#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.35"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.35:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.35:0.2"
msgid "4. Sumanavagga "
msgstr "4. With Sumanā "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.35:0.3"
msgid "35. Dānānisaṃsasutta "
msgstr "35. The Benefits of Giving "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.41, sc1
msgctxt "an5.35:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, dāne ānisaṃsā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are five benefits of giving. "

msgctxt "an5.35:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.35:1.3"
msgid "Bahuno janassa piyo hoti manāpo; "
msgstr "A giver, a donor is dear and beloved by many people. "

msgctxt "an5.35:1.4"
msgid "santo sappurisā bhajanti; "
msgstr "Good people associate with them. "

msgctxt "an5.35:1.5"
msgid "kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggacchati; "
msgstr "They get a good reputation. "

#. VAR: gihidhammā anapagato → gihidhammā anapeto (bj, pts1) | gihidhammamanupagato (mr)
msgctxt "an5.35:1.6"
msgid "gihidhammā anapagato hoti; "
msgstr "They don’t neglect a layperson’s duties. "

msgctxt "an5.35:1.7"
msgid "kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "

msgctxt "an5.35:1.8"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dāne ānisaṃsāti. "
msgstr "These are the five benefits of giving. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.35:2.1"
msgid "Dadamāno piyo hoti, "
msgstr "Giving, one is loved, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.35:2.2"
msgid "sataṃ dhammaṃ anukkamaṃ; "
msgstr "and follows the way of the good. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: sadā bhajanti → bhajanti sappurisā (sī )
msgctxt "an5.35:2.3"
msgid "Santo naṃ sadā bhajanti, "
msgstr "The good, disciplined spiritual practitioners "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.35:2.4"
msgid "saññatā brahmacārayo. "
msgstr "associate with you. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an5.35:3.1"
msgid "Te tassa dhammaṃ desenti, "
msgstr "They teach you the Dhamma "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.35:3.2"
msgid "Sabbadukkhāpanūdanaṃ; "
msgstr "that dispels all suffering. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.35:3.3"
msgid "Yaṃ so dhammaṃ idhaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding this teaching, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.35:3.4"
msgid "Parinibbāti anāsavo”ti. "
msgstr "you’re extinguished without defilements.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.35:3.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
